Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.00,0:01:47.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope Noah is okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.12,0:01:50.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If only we had a space suit for him, then he could tag along too!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.76,0:01:54.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't a cartoon. There's no budget for that kind of stuff in real life.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.99,0:01:57.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Says the company president's daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.01,0:01:58.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, cut it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.53,0:02:01.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if Noah's lonely...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.61,0:02:04.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been ages since we've seen Naru.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.68,0:02:43.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you. I can breathe painlessly now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.07,0:02:47.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.10,0:03:01.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is so weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.14,0:03:03.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I'm with you, it feels like a weight is lifted off my chest.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.29,0:03:06.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You aren't sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.35,0:03:10.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A part of the Scub Coral is merely growing inside you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.41,0:03:13.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you only kind to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.66,0:03:16.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kind? You mean me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.81,0:03:21.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You listen to everything I have to say, and you're always by my side.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.63,0:03:24.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't even done anything in return.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.87,0:03:28.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You and I are parts of the same being.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.43,0:03:32.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We seek truth together and reject this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.05,0:03:35.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You really are kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.52,0:03:40.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because you haven't killed Ao either.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.38,0:03:44.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fukai Ao...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.26,0:03:47.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He too will see the truth eventually.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.46,0:04:16.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.03,0:04:23.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What is this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.44,0:04:36.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Below the Headquarters is a facility that processed and reused various materials that are found left inside the Scub Coral.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.96,0:04:39.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe you have been briefed on this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.72,0:04:41.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OPD...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.25,0:04:45.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Gazelle Corps are an independent and free contractor unit.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.11,0:04:47.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe we are free to go wherever we want.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.64,0:04:50.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, 100% of your assets belongs to the company,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.87,0:04:53.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and we demand complete reports on your activities.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.43,0:04:55.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.15,0:05:00.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are merely investigating what that USA agent was sniffing about.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.89,0:05:03.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As a precaution, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.25,0:05:05.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This place is just the ruins of an old experiment area.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.28,0:05:07.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's sealed in fear of contamination.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.51,0:05:09.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Contamination?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.19,0:05:13.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And here I was thinking the Quartz would be stockpiled here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.24,0:05:16.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quartz? There's none of that here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.90,0:05:18.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you expect us to believe that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.78,0:05:21.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The teams are retrieving them every mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.65,0:05:24.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And yet there's none here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.15,0:05:42.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just can't get used to space.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.20,0:05:44.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, later.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.55,0:05:47.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.45,0:05:49.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's bringing the Quartz in.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.98,0:05:53.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The stuff from the Scub Coral? Is it all held here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.64,0:06:06.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Silicon?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.95,0:06:09.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a strategy to look after those who get space sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.84,0:06:11.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean, strategy?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.30,0:06:16.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like you made it right on time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.16,0:06:20.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A butler? Is that a butler?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.89,0:06:24.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Chief Hannah from the team Harlequin.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.46,0:06:30.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're Ao, right? I knew it the moment I saw you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.66,0:06:32.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not hard with his hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.07,0:06:34.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, Chief...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.56,0:06:36.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just call me Mama.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.00,0:06:37.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone calls me that here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.91,0:06:40.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mama...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.38,0:06:43.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heh, a real alien.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.29,0:06:44.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alien?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.50,0:06:47.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's have some tea then.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.70,0:06:49.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we should have our meeting first.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.63,0:06:51.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold your horses.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.34,0:06:52.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuuin...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.41,0:06:53.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.94,0:06:55.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ivica, you're having coffee, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.67,0:07:02.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is why I hate space.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.10,0:07:05.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This computer has a Georg too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.25,0:07:07.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am one and the same, Fukai Ao.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.76,0:07:11.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's because I'm not a computer but an operating sys—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.40,0:07:11.56,Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep, he's the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.96,0:07:14.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ao, come here and help yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.54,0:07:26.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That plan pretty much sounds like interplanetary war.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.90,0:07:28.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It would appear so.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.79,0:07:34.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think it's that easy to get authorization for something that can intercept ballistic missiles in outer space?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.29,0:07:36.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Authorization? There's no need for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.14,0:07:39.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've already hacked the connection.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.03,0:07:41.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Fire Cracker, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.27,0:07:44.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just reporting. Later.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.73,0:07:46.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,J. Johansson.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.49,0:07:52.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Professor Johansson committed suicide a few years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.87,0:07:58.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Johansson Book he left behind is considered a prophecy by many.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.13,0:08:01.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He had an adopted son.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.87,0:08:04.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That son is you, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.43,0:08:05.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.42,0:08:12.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Johansson said... this world is mistaken.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.14,0:08:21.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if a fusion explosion were to take place in space as a result of a Scub Burst,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.55,0:08:19.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's started.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.40,0:08:24.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it would have no effect on us on the surface.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.53,0:08:27.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, the Scub Coral has materialized in low orbit,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.37,0:08:31.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,an altitude with a great number of satellites.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.40,0:08:36.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A fusion explosion there would result in large amounts of debris.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.51,0:08:41.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because of this, the UN has requested \NGeneration Bleu to eliminate the Secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.47,0:08:43.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurray! This is nice indeed!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.75,0:08:47.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can deploy with the eyes of the whole world on us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.36,0:08:49.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A real international rescue.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.96,0:08:54.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And if we fail, our sponsors will be all gone in a flash.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.04,0:08:59.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why us? They are here too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.06,0:09:01.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Harlequin are special.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.81,0:09:02.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean like you—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.42,0:09:09.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The official line is that Team Harlequin is our backup.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.40,0:09:10.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the truth is...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.71,0:09:12.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They are the protectors of the Quartz!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.11,0:09:13.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Quartz?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.60,0:09:17.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if the Seven Days of Fire came and the world was burnt to ashes,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.64,0:09:19.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they would stay alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.37,0:09:22.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why several families live here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.19,0:09:23.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seven days of what?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.70,0:09:25.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not the part you should worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.85,0:09:27.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are really rumors like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.28,0:09:31.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if we all died, they would stay alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.63,0:09:33.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just hurry up already!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.76,0:09:39.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our units have limited mobility in space.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.68,0:09:42.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We only have one shot to take it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.24,0:09:44.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ao, are you okay? Ao?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.45,0:09:48.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's strange... Why...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.86,0:09:51.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the first time...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.55,0:09:54.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't see the path of the wind.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.16,0:09:57.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.26,0:09:58.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the meaning of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.26,0:09:59.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ao, return immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.83,0:10:02.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fleur and Elena, stay on standby.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.90,0:10:03.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be good kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.84,0:10:05.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the ETA of the Secret is—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.58,0:10:07.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mama's words are absolute here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.04,0:10:22.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this path of the wind?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.85,0:10:24.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've seen it all my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.86,0:10:28.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since I'd first flown when I was little.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.14,0:10:29.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seen what?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.70,0:10:33.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've always piloted FPs following it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.39,0:10:39.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... everybody can see it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.59,0:10:46.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is probably how Ao sees the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.05,0:10:50.14,Default,,0000,0000,0150,,What he sees is not wind, it's trapar.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.14,0:10:52.05,Default,,0000,0000,0150,,He can see trapar?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.05,0:10:58.30,Default,,0000,0000,0150,,It's been revealed that parts of the DNA in his optic nerves are different from ours, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.30,0:11:02.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But trapar are just particles, only...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.15,0:11:06.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,25 nanometer in diameter. No human can see them with the naked eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.28,0:11:09.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But he can see them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.03,0:11:12.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why he could play such an active role.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.39,0:11:13.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.88,0:11:18.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you know so much about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.75,0:11:22.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because you're an alien.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.06,0:11:26.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Elena. Have you ever seen trapar?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.87,0:11:28.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, my ears can discern who the VA is for an anime character!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.38,0:11:33.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That means he sees the world differently from us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.80,0:11:35.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That sounds like a line from an anime.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.10,0:11:37.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not that I know of.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.03,0:11:41.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thirteen years ago, on the 12th April, Japanese time...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.80,0:11:47.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,12th of April?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.85,0:11:49.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haven't you heard?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.52,0:11:55.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nirvash!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.06,0:11:59.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Americans stationed in Okinawa scrambled instantly.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.09,0:12:00.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They recorded this footage.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.90,0:12:03.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.42,0:12:09.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Showing him this out of the blue...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.23,0:12:12.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We should've told you earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.16,0:12:17.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As you can see, the Mark I, AKA Nirvash, emerged from the pillar of light.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.00,0:12:19.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like the Scub Coral and the Secrets.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.69,0:12:22.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From another world.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.08,0:12:23.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Another world?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.73,0:12:24.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.18,0:12:26.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,According to Johansson...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.76,0:12:29.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't quote that quack scientist!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.04,0:12:32.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Where is my mother now?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.96,0:12:36.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've told you before. No one has seen her in over a decade...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.79,0:12:38.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you keeping it a secret?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.46,0:12:43.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After the Scub Burst near Okinawa, just the Nirvash was found without its pilot.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.86,0:12:50.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The alien you call Eureka is probably—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.85,0:12:58.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As there is close to no trapar in space,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.22,0:13:00.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it's inadvisable to dispatch Ao here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.75,0:13:03.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It would be dangerous to make him take part in the action.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.95,0:13:07.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As I have suggested previously, he should stay on board of the Protheus
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.62,0:13:10.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,under our custody and assist us in our research.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.00,0:13:13.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So even though this battle is in space, you went out of your way to request aid from Pied Piper
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.66,0:13:15.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,just so you can take Ao away from us?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.34,0:13:16.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take away?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.45,0:13:18.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what you're doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.95,0:13:22.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm opposed to having Ao take part in the fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.71,0:13:26.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He might be fighting his own kin!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.40,0:13:29.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mama... Chief...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.85,0:13:33.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as you're here, you're one of my children too. Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.98,0:13:37.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.71,0:13:38.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ao!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.65,0:13:42.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll show you I can fly.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.72,0:13:50.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ao, I'll guide you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.26,0:13:53.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet he's just going to go for a direct attack with a rocket punch anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.88,0:13:56.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, both of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.11,0:14:04.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyrie and Alleluiah will restrain the Secret's attacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.54,0:14:07.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nirvash will take that chance to attack the Secret,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.97,0:14:10.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,destroy it at close range,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.11,0:14:12.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and use its recoil to change its trajectory.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.16,0:14:16.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He will make contact, or rather, slam into the gigantic Scub Coral,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.20,0:14:21.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,drop speed, change course, and meet up with the Triton.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.74,0:14:24.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that all he can do with a full tank?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.76,0:14:28.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If he misses the Scub, he'll be headed straight home.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.57,0:14:31.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that happens, we'll bail him out with the Triton.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.51,0:14:37.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that the Secret?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.98,0:14:42.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's approaching the Scub with the same vector ever since it emerged.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.88,0:14:48.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I detect no propelling features, so we can presume it won't change course.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.95,0:14:57.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't count on trapar in space.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.33,0:14:59.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It appears the Secret has detected us already.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.79,0:15:01.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be very careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.75,0:15:03.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like a jack in the box.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.26,0:15:12.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll draw its attention with some July 4th fireworks!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.65,0:15:13.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.44,0:15:24.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stage two rockets, active!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.34,0:15:28.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Ao!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.40,0:15:35.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I really an alien?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.49,0:15:39.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Mom was one, then I'm also...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.84,0:15:42.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where am I from?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.38,0:15:45.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me, Secret!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.02,0:16:00.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ao!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.79,0:16:03.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! We're nearly out of fuel as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.73,0:16:19.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please change your vector to rendezvous with the Scub.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.23,0:16:19.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.70,0:16:29.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Pick up Alleluiah and Kyrie, and move to the rendezvous point with Nirvash!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.37,0:16:30.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.08,0:16:31.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.35,0:16:38.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A railgun?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.74,0:16:40.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a Japanese satellite!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.18,0:16:42.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A malfunction? Now they've done it...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.61,0:16:52.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.64,0:16:53.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.99,0:16:57.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Scub changed course and started falling.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.59,0:17:00.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Its speed vector is the same direction as the Nirvash's.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.85,0:17:02.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So what does that mean?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.50,0:17:09.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My course didn't change.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.80,0:17:13.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because we were moving in the same direction,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.60,0:17:17.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nirvash, the smaller mass of the two, merely slowed down.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.71,0:17:19.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The course of the two objects won't change.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.00,0:17:23.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now the gravity of the Earth will pull us down together.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.54,0:17:25.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's simply the conservation of momentum.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.95,0:17:26.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.81,0:17:29.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nirvash won't stop falling!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.13,0:17:30.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ao, get away from the Scub!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.73,0:17:31.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ao!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.50,0:17:33.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's falling...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.87,0:17:36.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fukai Ao...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.64,0:17:38.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I kind?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.55,0:17:44.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've got the course computed!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.37,0:17:49.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're falling into the atmosphere...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.90,0:17:52.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Scub Coral will burn away
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.11,0:17:56.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and thank goodness there are no satellites in the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.64,0:17:59.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't need to worry about the debris.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.12,0:18:04.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the Nirvash won't be able to endure the high temperature and will burn away.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.73,0:18:07.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want that! Do something, Papa!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.90,0:18:11.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fleur, wait for the Triton to pick you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.85,0:18:14.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You two can do nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.04,0:18:16.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you giving up on Ao?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.16,0:18:17.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because he's an alien?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.19,0:18:17.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fleur!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.40,0:18:20.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.67,0:18:28.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was impossible after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.81,0:18:30.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not your fault, Mama.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.04,0:18:33.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ao, when you enter the stratosphere, there will be trapar.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.61,0:18:35.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You may be able to use that to decelerate.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.22,0:18:38.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if I burn away first...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.65,0:18:39.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.87,0:18:40.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.09,0:18:43.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom isn't around anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.01,0:18:46.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are all kind to me but Mom's already gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.90,0:18:48.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you kept that a secret from me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.64,0:18:50.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So what?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.73,0:18:53.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not going to let you die.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.23,0:18:56.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I have to burn the Triton away, I'll save you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.65,0:18:58.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're coming for you! Just wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.58,0:19:03.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... I am...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.79,0:19:10.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ao...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.77,0:19:31.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry, Ao! Inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.69,0:19:48.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.18,0:20:05.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A ship?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.14,0:20:46.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it telling me to use the ship as a board?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.71,0:21:23.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's fly!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.45,0:22:14.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Eureka.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.39,0:22:15.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.54,0:22:19.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Your hair is...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.22,0:22:22.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M... Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.60,0:22:25.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To be continued.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.66,0:24:03.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time on Eureka Seven AO.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.91,0:24:08.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ao unexpectedly gets to spend time with his mother on the Gekko.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.13,0:24:11.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ao is confused by her eccentricity.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.22,0:24:16.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The truth she tells wakes a storm that shakes this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.68,0:24:21.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eureka Seven AO, episode 13: She's a Rainbow.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.69,0:24:24.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to the voices of the children of the stars.
